stimulus:
In this task you will see black or white beads being pulled from jars.

On each trial, a bead will be pulled from one of two jars. Once you see this bead, your goal is to predict the color of NEXT bead that will be pulled.

Every time you correctly guess the color of the NEXT bead, you will get a point. The more points you get, the higher your win bonus at the end of the experiment

Press the SPACEBAR to continue.

There are two types of jars:

1) Jars filled with ONLY white or black beads

2) Jars filled with 90% white or black beads and 10% of the opposite color mixed in

Press the SPACEBAR to continue.
